@page "/privacy-policy"

@layout MainLayout
<MudPaper Class="pa-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" GutterBottom="true">Privacy Policy</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        <b>Effective Date</b>: 2024
    </MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
        Thank you for accessing our open-source project. This privacy policy applies to our demonstration application, which is intended solely for showcasing project functionality and demonstrating features.
    </MudText>
    <MudDivider Class="my-4" />

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="py-2">1. Data Collection and Usage</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
        Our application does not collect or store any real user personal data. All data displayed (e.g., names, emails, transaction records) are dummy data generated solely for demonstration purposes.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="py-2">2. Data Security</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
        As this application is for demonstration only, the displayed data is virtual and not stored or transmitted to any servers.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="py-2">3. Open-Source Declaration</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
        This project is open-source, and its source code is publicly available. Anyone can review the code to confirm that no real data collection or privacy-infringing logic exists.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="py-2">4. Contact</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
        If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us: neo.js.cn@gmail.com
    </MudText>
</MudPaper>


